ture visual, AI agent map, business outcome levers, demo preview, ROI/value levers without fake percentages, Talk to Agent CTA, related platforms and capabilities. Financial Services challenges: legacy systems, compliance pressure, fragmented data, manual documentation, risk visibility. Banking challenges: customer service scale, compliance review, knowledge fragmentation, manual back-office processes, product/policy search. Insurance challenges: claims operations, policy search, risk assessment, document-heavy workflows, customer response time. Use agents such as Compliance Assistant, Customer Intelligence Agent, Risk Review Agent, Knowledge Search Agent, Executive Dashboard Agent, Banking Knowledge Agent, Relationship Manager Copilot, Contract Intelligence Agent, Claims Triage Agent, Policy Intelligence Agent, Underwriting Copilot. No fake clients, fake logos, fake ROI, or guarantees. Use clean graphics, carousels/tabs, Framer Motion if available, and responsive mobile layouts. Run lint/build.\"\n153 |   },\n154 |   {\n155 |     \"id\": \"19-industries-batch2-health-education\",\n156 |     \"title\": \"Design Healthcare Life Sciences Education pages\",\n157 |     \"scope\": \"page-family-design\",\n158 |     \"target\": \"Industries batch 2\",\n159 |     \"allowLandingChanges\": false,\n160 |     \"prompt\": \"Upgrade /industries/healthcare, /industries/life-sciences, and /industries/education using the same premium industry family design but tailored visuals and content. Do not touch landing page. Healthcare challenges: operational complexity, patient communication workflows, staff knowledge access, administrative burden, compliance-sensitive processes. Life Sciences challenges: research documentation, regulatory workflows, knowledge management, trial operations support, cross-functional collaboration. Education challenges: student support, faculty enablement, knowledge access, university operations, AI labs and learning platforms. Suggested agents: Care Operatio